### Get all characters
GET http://localhost:5555/api/characters

### Get character by ID
GET http://localhost:5555/api/characters/2

### Create a new character (Warrior)
POST http://localhost:5555/api/characters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hero_Warrior",
  "job": "WARRIOR"
}

### Create a new character (Mage)
POST http://localhost:5555/api/characters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Magic_User",
  "job": "MAGE"
}

### Create a new character (Thief)
POST http://localhost:5555/api/characters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Silent_Rogue",
  "job": "THIEF"
}

### Update character
PUT http://localhost:5555/api/characters/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated_Hero",
  "job": "MAGE"
}

### Delete character
DELETE http://localhost:5555/api/characters/1


